    <section class="project">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="large-8 large-offset-2 columns">
                <p>After scanning page after page of Bradbury's <i>Inspirations</i> spreads, my timeline's format began to take shape. Using the CYMK color pallate and three panel spreads, I borrowed from Bradbury's own techniques used during his time as Art Director for the publication. Inspired by <i>Inspirations</i> (hah!) I again chose to design in the spirit of Bradbury Thompson, using two of his favorites: Baskerville and Futura. The timeline itself highlights Bradbury's lfe events under Magenta, other artist's lives under Yellow, and historical events under Cyan.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

